"2976352402" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The default SSID is on the router label. The FCC manual states the default SSID is '''On Networks'''.
On Networks N150 router is a rebranded [[Netgear]] device in a different :casing, similar to the [[Netgear WNR2000v3]] with less LAN ports.
[https://wiki.openwrt.org/toh/netgear/wnr612v2 OpenWRT], DD-WRT and Gargoyle work with this device. {{see also|Netgear WNR612v2}}
